data-mypid=\"77\">ご挨拶</a></li> \n              <li class=\" c-left\"><a href=\"../company_profile/index1.html\" data-pid=\"78\">企業概要</a> \n               <ul> \n                <li class=\" c-left\"><a href=\"../company_profile/index1.html#profile\" data-pid=\"78\">会社概要</a></li> \n                <li class=\" c-left\"><a href=\"../company_profile/index1.html#history\" data-pid=\"78\">沿革</a></li> \n                <li class=\" c-left\"><a href=\"../company_profile/index1.html#maker\" data-pid=\"78\">取り扱いメーカー</a></li> \n               </ul></li> \n              <li class=\" c-left\"><a href=\"../Activities/index.html\" data-pid=\"123\">事業案内</a></li> \n              <li class=\" c-left\"><a href=\"../base/location.html\" data-pid=\"103\">事業所一覧</a></li> \n              <li class=\" c-left\"><a href=\"../Product_guide/product01.html\" data-pid=\"90\">取扱商品</a></li> \n              <li class=\" c-left\"><a href=\"../festa2022/index.html\" data-pid=\"79\">ツールdeフェスタ</a></li> \n              <li class=\" c-left\"><a href=\"https://job-gear.net/sankotech/\">採用情報</a></li> \n              <li class=\" c-left\"><a href=\"../Information/index.html\" data-pid=\"122\">お問い合わせ</a></li> \n              <li class=\" c-left\"><a href=\"../info.html\" data-pid=\"72\">Information</a> \n               <ul> \n                <li class=\" c-left\"><a href=\"../info.html\" data-pid=\"72\">新着情報</a></li> \n                <li class=\" c-left\"><a href=\"../stj.html\" data-pid=\"73\">STジャーナル</a></li> \n               </ul></li> \n             </ul> \n            </div> \n           </div> \n           <div id=\"spNavigationTrigger\" class=\" c-sp_navigation_btn\"></div> \n          </nav> \n         </div> \n        </div> \n       </section> \n      </div> \n     </header> \n    </div> \n    <div id=\"a-billboard\" class=\"a-billboard    cssskin-_area_billboard\"> \n     <div class=\"site_frame\"> \n      <section> \n       <div id=\"bk1682\" class=\"b-plain c-space_normal c-sp-space_normal c-sp-padding_normal cssskin-_block_billboard\" data-bk-id=\"bk1682\"> \n        <div class=\" column -column1\"> \n         <div class=\" c-body\"> \n          <div class=\"c-img   \"> \n           <picture> \n            <source type=\"image/webp\" srcset=\"../_src/1143/img20190925104003839067.webp?v=1699359480286\"> \n            <img src=\"../_src/1143/img20190925104003839067.jpg?v=1699359480286\" width=\"1000\" height=\"300\" alt=\"\" id=\"imgsrc1143_1\" loading=\"lazy\"> \n           </picture> \n          </div> \n         </div> \n        </div> \n       </div> \n      </section> \n     </div> \n    </div> \n    <main> \n     <div id=\"a-site_contents\" class=\"a-site_contents  noskin\"> \n      <article> \n       <div class=\"site_frame\"> \n        <div class=\"g-column\"> \n         <div id=\"a-main\" class=\"a-main column -col12 \"> \n          <section> \n           <div id=\"bk1683\" class=\"b-plain c-space_normal c-sp-space_normal c-sp-padding_normal cssskin-_block_main\" data-bk-id=\"bk1683\"> \n            <div class=\" column -column1\" id=\"profile\"> \n             <h4 class=\" c-small_headline c-left\"><span style=\"color:#434343;\" class=\" d-larger_font\">ご挨拶</span></h4> \n             <div class=\" c-body c-left\">\n               &nbsp; \n             </div> \n             <div class=\" c-body c-left\"> \n              <span style=\"color:#434343;\">　社会はテクノロジーの進化をエネルギーとして成長し続けてきました</span> \n             </div> \n             <div class=\" c-body c-left\"> \n              <span style=\"color:#434343;\">　そして今、私たちが生きる21世紀は大きな変革の時期を迎えています</span> \n             </div> \n             <div class=\" c-body c-left\"> \n              <span style=\"color:#434343;\">&nbsp;</span> \n             </div> \n             <div class=\" c-body c-left\"> \n              <span style=\"color:#434343;\">　技術革新が加速するビジネス環境にあって</span> \n             </div> \n             <div class=\" c-body c-left\"> \n              <span style=\"color:#434343;\">　サンコーテックは多様化するお客様のニーズに迅速に対応すべく、</span> \n             </div> \n             <div class=\" c-body c-left\"> \n              <span style=\"color:#434343;\">　最新鋭の豊富な商品ラインナップと永年培ったノウハウで提案型トータルコンサルティングを展開中です</span> \n             </div> \n             <div class=\" c-body c-left\"> \n              <span style=\"color:#434343;\">&nbsp;</span> \n             </div> \n             <div class=\" c-body c-left\"> \n              <span style=\"color:#434343;\">　レンタル事業部門においては、</span> \n             </div> \n             <div class=\" c-body c-left\"> \n              <span style=\"color:#434343;\">　ご提供する機材への様々な気遣いこそが、お客様の期待する成果に繋がるものと捉え、</span> \n             </div> \n             <div class=\" c-body c-left\"> \n              <span style=\"color:#434343;\">　「遣い手であるお客様に使っていただけるよう」サービスの充実を推進してまいります</span> \n             </div> \n             <div class=\" c-body c-left\"> \n              <span style=\"color:#434343;\">&nbsp;</span> \n             </div> \n             <div class=\" c-body c-left\"> \n              <span style=\"color:#434343;\">　企業理念は、「評価はお客様が下す」</span> \n             </div> \n             <div class=\" c-body c-left\"> \n              <span style=\"color:#434343;\">&nbsp;</span> \n             </div> \n             <div class=\" c-body c-left\"> \n              <span style=\"color:#434343;\">　未来志向のプラントエンジニアリングサポーターとして</span> \n             </div> \n             <div class=\" c-body c-left\"> \n              <span style=\"color:#434343;\">　サンコーテックは全国の事業拠点でお客様からご評価をいただけるよう</span> \n             </div> \n             <div class=\" c-body c-left\"> \n              <span style=\"color:#434343;\">　地域に根ざした活動を推進してまいります</span> \n             </div> \n            </div> \n           </div> \n           <div id=\"bk1684\" class=\"b-plain c-space_normal c-sp-space_normal c-sp-padding_normal cssskin-_block_main\" data-bk-id=\"bk1684\"> \n            <div class=\" column -column1\"> \n             <div class=\" c-body c-right\"> \n              <div class=\"c-img   \"> \n               <picture> \n                <source type=\"image/webp\" srcset=\"../_src/1097/img20180712094226535589.webp?v=1699359480286\"> \n                <img src=\"../_src/1097/img20180712094226535589.png?v=1699359480286\" width=\"866\" height=\"1000\" alt=\"\" id=\"imgsrc1097_1\" class=\" c-no_adjust\" loading=\"lazy\"> \n               </picture> \n              </div>&nbsp; 　　　　 \n             </div> \n             <div class=\" c-body c-right\"> \n              <span class=\" d-small_font\">サンコーテック株式会社 代表取締役 　</span> \n              <span class=\" d-large_font\"><span class=\" d-small_font\">髙橋　桂</span>　 　　</span> \n             </div> \n            </div> \n           </div> \n          </section> \n         </div> \n        </div> \n       </div> \n      </article> \n     </div> \n    </main> \n    <div id=\"a-footer\" data-float=\"false\" class=\"a-footer   cssskin-_area_footer\"> \n     <footer> \n      <div class=\"site_frame\"> \n       <div id=\"bk5102\" class=\"b-plain c-space_normal c-sp-space_normal c-sp-padding_normal cssskin-_block_footer\" data-bk-id=\"bk5102\"> \n        <div class=\" column -column1\"> \n         <div class=\" c-body c-center\">\n           &nbsp; \n         </div> \n         <div class=\" c-body c-right\"> \n          <span class=\"bindicon-arrow-up2\"></span> \n          <a href=\"index.html\" data-mypid=\"77\">ページトップへ</a> \n         </div> \n        </div> \n       </div> \n       <div id=\"bk1689\" class=\"b-plain c-space_normal c-sp-space_normal c-sp-padding_normal cssskin-_block_footer\" data-bk-id=\"bk1689\" data-shared=\"true\" data-sharedname=\"フッター\"> \n        <div class=\" column -column1\"> \n         <div class=\" c-body c-right\"> \n          <hr class=\"c-hr\"> \n         </div> \n         <div class=\" c-body c-center\"> \n          <div class=\"c-img   \"> \n           <picture> \n            <source type=\"image/webp\" srcset=\"../_src/6484/logo-credit-500.webp?v=1699359480286\"> \n            <img src=\"../_src/6484/logo-credit-500.p